{
  "texts": [
    "The terms leaking and intake are dominant, and records from the MWOs that belong to Topic 1 could fall be annotated with code 7160.",
    "For Topic 2, the dominant terms are baffle, engine, and oil.",
    "The JASC code of 8550 pertains to Reciprocating Engine Oil System, so Topic 2 could be related to this code.",
    "Codes 7261-Turbine Engine Oil System, and 7900-Engine Oil System could also be appropriate annotations for the maintenance problems from this Topic 2.",
    "For the Topic 3, the terms intakes, compression, seal, engine, and baffle are dominant."
  ]
}